1 Hist orical Society for their work to honor Bob Wills and revive this
2 special celebration at the Capitol.
3 THAT a copy of this resolution be distributed to the Oklahoma
4 Arts Council, the Oklahoma Film and Music Office, and the Oklahoma
5 Historical Society.
6
7 DIRECT TO CALENDAR.
